## ğŸ“¦ Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/react-meals-app.git

# Navigate into the project folder
cd react-meals-app

# Navigate into the project folder
cd backend

# Install backend dependencies
npm install

# Start the backend
npm start  

# Open another terminal and navigate into the project folder
cd react-meals-app

# Install frontend dependencies
npm install

# Start the frontend
npm run dev